name: Silver Urban Glam Watch
description:
Our designer inspired Silver Urban Glam Watch is stylish and simply stunning. Mix it with other bracelets & bangles for an irresistible arm party.

Links are removable for custom sizing by a jeweler.

Features: 
A single row of rhinestones surrounding the face
3 non-functioning sub-dials 
Hands with luminescent accents 
Numbers and line indices 
Water and dust resistant 
Case: stainless steel 
Caseback: stainless steel 
Bracelet: stainless steel links 
Clasp: push-button deployment 
Japanese quartz movement 
Face measurements: 40mm W x 40mm L x 12mm thickness 
Bracelet measurements: 20mm W x 8.25"L 
Weight: 4.2oz

**We will not accept exchanges on watches that have had the protective plastic removed from the band.
